

#  To create run config:

    Run  ->  Run Configurations

    choose "Java Application"
    choose New (left most icon at top of config list)

    fill in dialog and save

    can be run here via lower right run button

#  To run the config without all the above (after it has been created)

    click run icon in tool bar (the Run button above tool bar does not 
      include the config I did above).

    the down arrow to right of run
      icon (white arrow in green filled circle)
      the down arrow just right of icon allows selecting from
      run configs
